Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Iceberg Lake, Glacier National Park
Description: The final destination of an extremely strenuous, hours-long hike in Glacier National Park, Montana. Witnessing it is worth the strife it takes to get there.

Name: Mammoth Mountain California
Description: Fun spot in the winter for snow sports and seeing snow capped peaks.

Name: Chantilly Ice Cream Laguna Beach
Description: A quaint ice cream shop located in a quirky, art-infused Californian beach town. The ice cream is nothing special, but the memories make it special!

Name: Main Street, Ventura
Description: The core of Downtown Ventura, a beach town that embodies every characteristic of California.

Name: Philz Coffee, Palo Alto
Description: Coffee shop that sells delicious coffee with a beautiful seating area, shaded by trees.
